maml:description.maml:para: Creates a new App Volumes Manager Session.
Creates a new App Volumes Manager Session.

dev:remarks.maml:para: Open the session with AppVolumes Manager
You can omit the parameter names

maml:description.maml:para: Closes an existing App Volumes Manager Session.
Closes an existing App Volumes Manager Session.

command:example.maml:title: -------------------------- Example 1 --------------------------
command:example.dev:code:
Open-AppVolSession -Uri "http://appvol.domain.com" -Username "admin" -Password "Password1"
# Logoff from the App Volumes manager. Close-AppVolSession
